
    Diddy pays tribute to Kim Porter

        

    
        
                
                Image copyright
                 Getty Images
                
            
            
            Image caption
                
                    Kim Porter and Diddy in 2009
                
            Diddy has paid tribute to his ex Kim Porter, who died last week.The American rapper said they "were more than soulmates" in a series of emotional posts on Twitter and Instagram.The model and actress was 47 and was the mother to three of Diddy's children.Numerous celebrities including Rihanna, 50 Cent and Missy Elliott paid tribute to her last week, but this is the first time Diddy has broken his silence.
    
        
