        Kim and Diddy dated on and off until 2007 and had three children together: twins Jessie James and D'Lila, 11, and son Christian, 20.She had acted in films like 2001's The Brothers and in the US TV show Wicked Wicked Games.The cause of her death is unknown.Follow Newsbeat on Instagram, Facebook and Twitter.Listen to Newsbeat live at 12:45 and 17:45 every weekday on BBC Radio 1 and 1Xtra - if you miss us you can listen back here.
            

